-- Norway's finmin keeps bank countercyclical buffer unchanged 
-- 
-- Fri Apr 04, 2014 02:30AM EDT
-- None



OSLO, April 4 (Reuters) - The level of the countercyclical capital buffer for Norwegian banks should remain unchanged, in line with advice from the central bank, the finance ministry said on Friday.

Last December, the ministry decided that banks had to hold a buffer of 1 percent from June 2015.